question: Hi All:I've had diabetes for 2 years, and taking an ACE inhibitor the entire time, and never had any kidney issues until recently.  A few months ago I was also diagnosed with lupus, and started treatment immediately.  A couple of weeks ago, I had lab work done which included a urine sample, which showed there was a trace of blood and 30 mg/dl of protein in my urine.  Should I be concerned?Thanks in advance for any insight!
title: Here's a new protein in urine question!
